Sales Operations & KPI Performance Dashboard (Excel)

This project simulates an operational reporting environment where transactional sales data is validated, structured, and transformed into KPI-driven insights to support business operations. It focuses on ensuring data reliability, enabling performance visibility, and supporting decision-making through structured reporting.

Project Overview

Domain: Sales operations
Tool: Microsoft Excel
Focus: Data quality, KPI reporting, operational performance tracking

Dashboard Preview

Workflow

Validated and structured raw data to ensure consistency and usability
Standardized business dimensions (channels, categories, order status)
Prepared dataset for reliable KPI tracking and reporting
Developed pivot-based analytical views
Built an interactive dashboard

Key Deliverables

KPI reporting dashboard
Channel and category performance tracking
Customer segmentation insights
Order status monitoring

Data Quality & Controls

Ensured consistency across fields
Handled missing and inconsistent data
Standardized inputs
Structured data for reporting

Business Impact

Improved visibility into performance
Identified high-performing segments
Provided operational insights
Supported decision-making

Key Business Insights

• Female customer segment contributes significantly to overall sales
• High delivery success rate reflects efficient operations
• Demand concentrated in key states like Maharashtra
• Amazon dominates as primary sales channel
• Sets and Kurtas drive major revenue
• March and August are peak sales periods

How to Use

Open sales_operations_dashboard.xlsx
Use filters to explore data
Review KPIs and trends

Skills Demonstrated

Data Quality Validation
KPI Reporting
Operational Data Analysis
Business Process Support
Reporting & Communication

